726721f-a.title: Queens: Fresh Meadow Lane - 65th Avenue
726721f-a.text:
Fresh Meadow Lane, at 65th Avenue, looking north across
the latter. This area was known as Flushing Heights (1909
map) and the Lane was named Market Street. Note the smithy
on the left.
P. L. Sperr  April 6, 1927
